‐ I can't help
that I'm Harry's only friend.

16:36.693 --> 16:38.797
‐ Maybe he should
have some more.

16:38.797 --> 16:40.567
We're a great town.

16:40.567 --> 16:43.472
If he can't see the value
of humans here,

16:43.472 --> 16:46.445
