18:41.576 --> 18:43.880
That can't be right.
‐ Come on, Deputy.

18:43.880 --> 18:45.449
I thought you took
a lipreading workshop.

18:45.449 --> 18:48.288
‐ I could only afford
the first three classes,

18:48.288 --> 18:51.596
but I get lots of practice
at family gatherings.

18:51.596 --> 18:55.336
My grandma talks a lot
of shit about me.

18:57.140 --> 18:59.679
‐ We're not answering
any of your questions

18:59.679 --> 19:01.783
