19:11.703 --> 19:13.472
‐ I'm not your puppet.

19:13.472 --> 19:14.809
‐ I'll do it.
I'll be your puppet.

19:14.809 --> 19:16.546
‐ No, not you.

19:16.546 --> 19:19.852
