a Patience tourism commercial.

24:09.565 --> 24:10.834
♪ ♪

24:10.834 --> 24:12.804
This little guy, huh?

24:12.804 --> 24:14.207
♪ ♪

24:14.207 --> 24:16.244
‐ Oh, my.
