so I need you

25:02.838 --> 25:04.908
to find the realtor
that was handling the deal.

25:04.908 --> 25:06.912
And then we need to set up
an undercover recon mission.

25:06.912 --> 25:08.081
Do you copy?

25:08.081 --> 25:09.852
[honks horn]
Okay, good.

25:09.852 --> 25:13.593
Deputy, it's time for a little
unofficial sheriff's business,

25:13.593 --> 25:16.197
so you might want
to get off this channel

25:16.197 --> 25:18.803
for just a couple minutes.

25:18.803 --> 25:21.809
[car honks]

25:21.809 --> 25:24.615
[upbeat music]

25:24.615 --> 25:29.057
‐ Candle equipment.

25:29.057 --> 25:33.165
‐ That's not a real IOU.
