25:45.657 --> 25:49.732
And with these cards,
I cannot lose.

25:49.732 --> 25:53.071
‐ You lose.
‐ So do you.

25:53.071 --> 25:54.975
Thanks for your money.

25:54.975 --> 25:56.879
You can keep
your bathrobe candle.

25:56.879 --> 25:58.716
♪ ♪

25:58.716 --> 26:00.787
