26:41.034 --> 26:43.004
for a satellite
radio station nearby.

26:43.004 --> 26:45.710
I'm also a licensed pilot,
and I'm a horse rancher.

26:45.710 --> 26:49.350
‐ Huh, okay, quite a life.
